Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:05.60,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Karuizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:17.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yes! Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:18.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That's just like Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:20.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:23.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Too bad about the tennis,\Nbut bowling's also fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:29.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Well, there's also one guy who is drinking in desperation\Nbecause he can't watch tennis girls in miniskirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're up next, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:33.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:34.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:35.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:40.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And? Who is it? The person\Nyou wanted me to meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:42.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:46.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who was waiting in the pouring rain at the tennis court for 4 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:49.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ging into dry clothes\Nright now and will then come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:52.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop beating around the bush and just spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:55.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is coming here on a bike in this rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:01.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:06.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go at it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:13.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Jeet Kune Do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He dodged it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:26.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:27.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll knock you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:33.77,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We won't give in to the hot blazing sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.77,0:01:35.49,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A gallant and dashing deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:37.45,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A man Sonoko'll be pleased to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.70,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and an explosive situation at a bowling alley!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:41.21,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:42.95,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:45.45,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
